    "Name": "Nova",
    "Details": "Presenting the Quicsell Nova – Unleash the Inferno, MechWarriors! Our cutting-edge Mech comes equipped with heavy chem lasers, delivering superior damage and cost-efficient heat management. But here's the thrill – the more you fire, the hotter it gets. It's not a flaw; it's a feature! Embrace the strategic challenge of managing your firepower, and you'll own the battlefield. The Quicsell Nova – where the heat is on, and victory is sweeter when you earn it!  \n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Quicksell Clan Mech</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.04</color></b>\n\n<br><br><color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limits: Omni</color>\n\n",
